info:

  version: 1.0.0
paths:

    get:
      operationId: listVersionsv2
      summary: List API versions
      responses:

          description: 200 response
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                foo:

                        id: v2.0
                        links:

      - name: Authorization
        in: header
        description: ID of the API version
        required: true
        schema:
          type: integer
  /people/{id}:

      parameters: {}
      responses:
        "200":
          description: 200 response
  /users/{id}:
